Super excited to announce that our film, "Like Wolves", has received the Silver Award for Best Action Short, the Bronze Award for Best Crime Short, and an Honorable Mention for Best Acting Duo! Thank you @independentshortsawards for the opportunity to include our film amongst all the other works of talent this year! 🎬
